<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">When to use</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">Use this pattern when creating or amending insolvency practitioner bulletins.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">How to design using this pattern</h2>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Document type</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">Publication: guidance (with an HTML attachment)</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Publication</h3>

<h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Title</h4>

<p class="govuk-body">The title should be: Insolvency practitioner bulletin [issue number] [(year)]: [insert title]</p>
<p class="govuk-body">For example, Insolvency practitioner bulletin 9 (2024): changes to the insolvency customer services mailbox</p>

<h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Summary</h4>

<p class="govuk-body">Begin with:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>This bulletin explains ... [then read the document and summarise the content].</li>
  <li>This bulletin tells you about … [then read the document and summarise the content].</li>
  <li>This bulletin gives an update ... [then read the document and summarise the content].</li>
</ul>
<p class="govuk-body">For example, ‘This bulletin tells you about the new rules when sending emails to the mailbox, and how it will support you with repayments or refund requests.’</p>

<h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Details</h4>

<p class="govuk-body">Begin with:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>This bulletin explains [insert detail].</p>
  
  <p class="govuk-body">or</p>
  <li>This bulletin explains:<br>[detail]<br>[detail]</li>
</ul>
<p class="govuk-body">Then read the document and summarise the content to create the body text under the ‘Details’ section.</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Tagging content</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">No specific tagging guidance provided — confirm with content team if tagging is required for this pattern.</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">HTML attachment</h3>

<h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Title</h4>

<p class="govuk-body">[insert title] — Insolvency practitioner bulletin [issue number] [(year)]</p>
<p class="govuk-body">For example, Changes to the insolvency customer services mailbox — insolvency practitioner bulletin 9 (2024)</p>

<h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Body</h4>
<p class="govuk-body">Enter the contents of the bulletin. Do not include numbers in section headings.</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Collection</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">Add the URL of any new page to the relevant year of the HMRC insolvency practitioner bulletin collection. Do not create a public change note.</p>
